OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Cappear in court charged with spying
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThree Iranian men have appeared in
OL,8,Fcourt following an investigation by
OL,9,Fcounter terror police, as ITV News'
OL,10,FWill Tullis reports from Westminster
OL,11,FMagistrates' Court
OL,13,FThree Iranian men living in London
OL,14,Fhave appeared in court charged with
OL,15,Fspying offences on behalf of Iran's
OL,16,Fforeign intelligence service.
