OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Cappear in court charged with spying
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FMostafa Sepahvand, 39, Farhad Javadi
OL,8,FManesh, 44, and Shapoor Qalehali Khani
OL,9,FNoori, 55, appeared at Westminster
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday,
OL,11,Fcharged with offences under the
OL,12,FNational Security Act.
OL,14,FNo pleas were entered by the trio who
OL,15,Fwere all wearing grey sweatshirts,
OL,16,Fwith Sepahvand attending in a
OL,17,Fwheelchair and Noori hobbling into the
OL,18,Fdock.
