OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Cappear in court charged with spying
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FSepahvand is also charged with
OL,8,Fengaging in surveillance,
OL,9,Freconnaissance and open-source
OL,10,Fresearch, intending to commit acts,
OL,11,Fnamely serious violence against a
OL,12,Fperson in the UK.
OL,14,FManesh and Noori are further charged
OL,15,Fwith engaging in surveillance and
OL,16,Freconnaissance, with the intention
OL,17,Fthat acts, namely serious violence
OL,18,Fagainst a person in the UK, would be
OL,19,Fcommitted by others.
