OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Cappear in court charged with spying
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe trio were remanded into custody
OL,8,Fand will next appear for a preliminary
OL,9,Fhearing at the Old Bailey on June 6.
OL,11,FThe Home Secretary has said national
OL,12,Fsecurity powers must be strengthened
OL,13,Fin response.
OL,15,FYvette Cooper said: "I want to thank
OL,16,Fthe police and security services for
OL,17,Ftheir continuing work on this very
OL,18,Fserious investigation, and for their
OL,19,Fimmense dedication to protecting our
OL,20,Fnational security and the safety of
OL,21,Four communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
