OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Cappear in court charged with spying
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,F"The charges that have been laid
OL,8,Fagainst these three individuals must
OL,9,Fnow take their course through the
OL,10,Fcriminal justice system and nothing
OL,11,Fmust be done to prejudice the outcome
OL,12,Fof those proceedings.
OL,14,F"But we will also take separate action
OL,15,Fto address the very serious wider
OL,16,Fissues raised by this case.
OL,18,F"The police have confirmed that the
OL,19,Fforeign state to which these charges
OL,20,Frelate is Iran, and Iran must be held
OL,21,Fto account for its actions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
