OL,7,F"We must also strengthen our powers to
OL,8,Fprotect our national security as we
OL,9,Fwill not tolerate growing state
OL,10,Fthreats on our soil.
OL,12,F"As part of that process we will
OL,13,Fpublish next week the results of
OL,14,FJonathan Hall KC's review into the
OL,15,Fapplication of our counter-terrorism
OL,16,Fframework to modern-day state threats."
